{"lastModified":1772813624179,"uri":"c::16875063630::vessel::91a4d5a0-32d0-11ef-85f3-9dc1fbf5dd47","yachtType":["Motor"],"description":"Operating Area: Australia\n\nIn 2008, Moonen, the renowned Dutch yacht builder, delivered LITTLE PERLE, a 30-metre superyacht that promises adventure while exuding class and elegance.\n\nDesigned by Rene Van Der Velden on the exterior and styled by Art-Line on the interior, LITTLE PERLE serves as a sophisticated platform for superyacht charters.\n\nUpon entering the wide main salon, guests are greeted with comfortable seating and a spacious formal dining table. Aft of the yacht, al fresco dining facilities accommodate up to 9 people, offering unforgettable experiences in the outdoor environment. Up to the flybridge, guests can relax in the Jacuzzi, enjoy cocktails at the bar, and bask in the sun across the expansive deck space.\n\nLITTLE PERLE’s 4 cabins provide flexible accommodation for up to 9 guests overnight, including a Master cabin, VIP suite, and two Twin cabins – one featuring a Pullman, perfect for large families. The yacht’s cruising capacity extends to 36 guests.\n\nAs a complete platform for exploration and adventure, LITTLE PERLE creates a gateway to unforgettable memories. Led by an experienced captain, the well-traveled and experienced crew ensures that guests’ every need is met with a warm smile, making charters truly exceptional.","blueprint":{"name":"LITTLE PERLE","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::91a4d5a0-32d0-11ef-85f3-9dc1fbf5dd47::assets::f8f06dd0-6d46-11f0-b4ec-4126d86b0baa/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::91a4d5a0-32d0-11ef-85f3-9dc1fbf5dd47::assets::f8edd5c0-6d46-11f0-b4ec-4126d86b0baa/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::91a4d5a0-32d0-11ef-85f3-9dc1fbf5dd47::assets::f8eaa170-6d46-11f0-b4ec-4126d86b0baa/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::91a4d5a0-32d0-11ef-85f3-9dc1fbf5dd47::assets::f8e30050-6d46-11f0-b4ec-4126d86b0baa/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::